{"tid":496984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚！】青山剛昌聲明　垃圾漫畫《名偵探柯屎》長期休刊","createTime":"2017-12-12T09:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T12:15:09.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"913813f360273791dcced9853fc38a2dceece36a","tid":496984,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:14:47.000Z","msg":"2017/12/12 15:54<br />\n <br />\n（更新：新增影片）<br />\n日本人氣漫畫《名偵探柯南》傳出長期休刊，作者青山剛昌透過圖文表達，因身體健康因素將休載漫畫；消息一出，粉絲錯愕之餘，希望他養好病，「沒關係!為了柯南，我會等的」。<br />\n<br />\n《名偵探柯南》在日本漫畫雜誌《週刊少年Sunday》連載23年。《臉書》社團「米花町柯南情報處 Conan Intelligence Agency of Beika City」轉貼該週刊的聲明，是《柯南》作者青山剛昌以輕鬆的畫風宣布重大消息，全文譯文如下：<br />\n大家好，我是青山！<br />\n從下期開始，為了要養病和讓身體充電的關係，<br />\n將會進入長期休載。<br />\n今年我為了「唐紅的戀歌」、「魔術快斗」的「太陽的光暈」、1000話紀念的「深紅的修學旅行篇」等等等等......<br />\n已經將力氣全用在戀愛喜劇上，好像有點努力過頭了（笑）<br />\n可是這番努力是值得的對吧？<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;所以，我會暫時休息一下，要等我喔～♪<br />\n（漫畫對話）<br />\n青山：要開始玩「動物之森手遊版」了嗎...（笑）<br />\n灰原：要好好養病啊！！<br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"0d86123ac70481628b76ba54b0aeaad5cf69bf37","tid":496984,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20171212/1257852/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20171212%2F1257852%2F&d=yp2e5tveSbr5S2cn2sXZ1whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f2ede209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20171212%2F1257852%2F&h=146c4ce2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20171212/1257852/</a>"},{"pid":"1bd5fee9039bcea86cd8cb1a78141c9f6c477935","tid":496984,"uid":53122,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20171212/1257852/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20171212%2F1257852%2